+	 * <p>
+	 * If true (default is false), a URL encoded slash will be allowed in the
+	 * URL. Allowing encoded slashes can cause security vulnerabilities in some
+	 * situations depending on how the container constructs the
+	 * HttpServletRequest.
+	 * </p>
